    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The overall body of evidence supports acceptance of the FEA modeling framework for the non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending COU. All quantitative acceptance criteria were satisfied: E/uval below 1.96 and QoI differences below 10% for stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement across N=11 constructs. The model risk level of 3 is considered adequately addressed given the breadth of validation evidence collected. The assessment team is satisfied that the simulation results are sufficiently credible to support the regulatory submission.",
